    "details": {
      "biography": "<p>20&rsquo; tall humanoids with a single, central eye. Dwell in caves, alone or in small groups. Cultivate grapes and raise sheep.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Attack penalty: </strong>&ndash;2 penalty on all hit rolls, due to limited depth perception (already included in Attack Bonus).</li>\n<li><strong>Rock throwing:</strong> Up to 200&rsquo;.</li>\n<li><strong>Slow-witted: </strong>Can be tricked by clever PCs.</li>\n<li><strong>Curse:</strong> 1-in-20 cyclops can place a curse on a character once a week. Mental save or be afflicted by a curse of the referee&rsquo;s choosing. (Maximum possible effects: &ndash;2 penalty to saves, &ndash;4 penalty to hit, an ability score reduced by 50%.)</li>\n</ul>",
